## 📖 Overview

**StudyPilot** is an AI-powered study assistant designed to help students learn more effectively from study materials such as lecture notes, textbooks, and handwritten documents.

Users can upload study materials and instantly generate:

* 📝 Smart Notes
* 📚 Flashcards
* ❓ AI-generated Quizzes
* 💡 Topic Explanations

The system combines **Google Gemini AI**, **FastAPI**, **React**, and **Firebase** to provide an interactive learning experience.

---

# ✨ Features

* 📄 Image-based study material analysis
* 🤖 AI-generated study notes
* 🧠 Flashcard generation
* ❓ Multiple-choice quiz generation
* 💬 AI explanations for difficult concepts
* 🔥 Firebase Authentication
* ☁️ Firestore cloud database
* 📜 Automatic history storage
* 🔒 Secure user authentication using Firebase ID Tokens
* ⚡ FastAPI REST APIs
* 🎨 Responsive React frontend

---

# 🏗️ System Architecture

```text
                 React Frontend
                        │
                        │
                 POST /api/chat
                        │
                        ▼
                 FastAPI Backend
                        │
             Coordinator Router
                        │
      ┌─────────┬──────────┬────────────┬──────────┐
      │         │          │            │          │
   Notes     Quiz     Flashcards   Explainer
      │         │          │            │
      └─────────┴──────────┴────────────┘
                        │
                  Google Gemini
                        │
              AI Generated Response
                        │
                Firebase Firestore
                        │
              User Study History
```

